Extended Stay Application
Receive Your Extended Stay Application Today
Click the button below and complete the form to receive a copy of our extended stay application via email.
Applicants are Required to:
Complete the form at the link below to receive an application
Complete Full Application (Delivered via e-mail)
Pay for and Pass a Criminal Background & Credit Check ($50 each; All applicants over age of 18)
Obtain approval via the background check process.
Pay 1st Month’s rent to hold your site.
Receive Your Application for Extended Stay Today!
